cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for vehicle classification in automated toll systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics (cs.RO) as the proposed method can be used in portable computer vision systems for toll collection. The use of deep learning techniques for classification suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves 3D reconstruction and point cloud processing, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics).
